{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":609165,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"乱对弱势群体不一定有好处，对既得利益者一定没好处。国家总是处在国际环境中，乱起来可能会被收割。","timestamp":1606233272,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609174,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果真再有人报他……","timestamp":1606233396,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609181,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 我也不希望乱，但是如果稳定是通过对弱势群体的持续压制造成的，那么早晚有一天会压制不住","timestamp":1606233430,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609200,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 也不是完全压制，还是给一点糖吃的……让你下不了彻底反抗的决心","timestamp":1606233540,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609209,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 那是因为还在经济增长期","timestamp":1606233579,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609221,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 当局对形势的判断还是稳的，过了快速增长期就会调整政策了","timestamp":1606233653,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609230,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"洞主说的有理","timestamp":1606233696,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":609826,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 调整政策：指更高压，不加掩饰的暴力","timestamp":1606243075,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":610195,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 这个梦十多年前就不做了，真不知道你怎么说服自己相信的","timestamp":1606268433,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":612208,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 额","timestamp":1606296017,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":617585,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":126363,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"实现帝国境内所有阶层的谈判与和解\n更像长枪党","timestamp":1606393302,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":126363,"reply":11,"tag":"政治相关","text":"温和的社民（也就是dz本人）的理想是结束目前利维坦与资本合谋对劳动阶级吃干抹净的现状，实现帝国境内所有阶层的谈判与和解，给予弱势群体一些组织与抗争能力，而不是一味通过压制弱势群体而实现稳定。\n不知为何你校的理想主义者一张嘴就是“不能乱“这种极右味道浓到化不开的话语，可能铁拳没砸到自己头上，因为会多做几道题有了人上人幻觉？\n\n附今日新闻一则，大家体会一下什么叫对劳动阶级吃干抹净，以及弱势群体的无力与无奈：\n\n不知道你们还记不记得王攀，\n他又可以招生了。\n那个“长期让陶崇园送饭，打车、买车票、叫醒起床、找眼镜以及做其他与科研教学无关的事，并干预其出国读博、找工作等”“要求陶崇园叫他爸爸”的王攀，\n又可以招生了！\n\n\n#政治相关\n\n","timestamp":1606232923,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782654,"url":"","vote":{}}}